---
// Why These Two Component
---

<div class="bg-gray-50 py-16">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    
    <!-- Headline -->
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-4">
      Why These Are Our Top Recommendations
    </h2>
    
    <!-- Opening -->
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 text-center mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      After arranging 1,470 policies last year, 80% chose Swica or Helsana. Here's why:
    </p>

    <!-- 4 Key Reasons Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      
      <!-- Reason 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-red-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Superior English Support</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Both have dedicated English-speaking teams (Swica 24/7, Helsana business hours)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Reason 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-red-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
              <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
              <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
              <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Expat-Friendly Policies</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Understand international backgrounds, flexible with documentation</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Reason 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-red-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Comprehensive Coverage</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">Full range of models (HMO, GP, Standard) + excellent supplementary options</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Reason 4 -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm">
        <div class="flex items-start">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-8 w-8 text-red-600" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"></polygon>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="ml-4">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Proven Track Record</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600">5.4/6 (Swica) and 5.2/6 (Helsana) satisfaction ratings</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Insider Note Box -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-md border-l-4 border-red-600">
      <div class="flex items-start">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-red-600 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
          <line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12" y2="12"></line>
          <line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12.01" y2="8"></line>
        </svg>
        <div>
          <p class="text-gray-900 font-semibold mb-2">Insider Advantage</p>
          <p class="text-gray-700">As a FINMA-regulated broker, we get group discounts for both. You pay <span class="font-bold text-red-600">CHF 500-1,200/year LESS</span> than going direct - same coverage, better price.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Subtle CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-8">
      <button 
        onclick="window.openHealthModal('consultation')"
        class="text-red-600 hover:text-red-700 font-medium underline"
      >
        Want to see both rates? â†’ Book consultation
      </button>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

